com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.framework.utils

Class SCUIApplicationCacheHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.framework.utils.SCUIApplicationCacheHolder

  • public class SCUIApplicationCacheHolder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class should contain all the cached and static object which are specific to any application. This class should not be instantiated using the constructor; instead SCUIApplicationCacheManager#getCacheFor(SCUIContext) or SCUIApplicationCacheManager#getCacheFor(ServletContext) should be used to get an object. asmishra
